Interface Cytokine<T extends NervousSystemElement>

Type Parameters:

All Superinterfaces:

All Known Implementing Classes:

public interface Cytokine<T extends NervousSystemElement> extends NervousSystemElement
Interface representing a cytokine in the nervous system. A cytokine is a small protein important in cell signaling, and it can target various cells in the nervous system.

This interface defines the behavior of cytokines, including targeting, interaction, and lifecycle management.
